title: (PSX-PSP) Front Mission 3 converted properly (Kingdom-games by K
description:
FRONT MISSION 3:

Front Mission 3 is a turn-based strategy game with a Double Feature Scenario. It allows the player to choose one of two completely different viewpoints towards the same general plot of the game. Each scenario features 8 characters with their own unique robots.

After numerous wars and terrorist attacks, Yokosuka had finally entered a state of peace; it would last only 10 short years. A deadly explosion rocked the continent, disrupting peace and causing a worldwide panic.


Tested and working on all CFW's 5.00 m33 and above using the 500 popsloader pack set on 3.72 POPS...KloWn
